---
const {
  title = "UTYA",
  subtitle = "The Duck Everyone Knew, But No One Named",
  
} = Astro.props;
---

<style>
.black-4-widget {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 48px auto;
  color: white;
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive, sans-serif;
  text-align: center;
}

.black-4-widget h2 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.black-4-widget .subtitle {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: white;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.black-4-widget .card {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05));
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 24px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  margin-top: 32px;
  text-align: left;
  user-select: none;
}

.black-4-widget .card img {
  max-width: 100%;
  border-radius: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.black-4-widget .card-content {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #FFD700; /* رنگ زرد طلایی */
  text-align: center;
}

/* بخش جدید برای توضیح utaya کیه */
.utya-info {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 48px;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  text-align: left;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #eee;
}

.utya-info img {
  width: 10rem; 
  border-radius: 16px;
}

.utya-info-text {
  flex: 1;
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive, sans-serif;
  font-weight: 500;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .black-4-widget h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .utya-info {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .utya-info img {
    width: 80%;
    max-width: 300px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
}
</style>

<div class="black-4-widget">
  <h2>{title}</h2>
  <div class="subtitle">{subtitle}</div>

  <div class="card">
    <img src="/about-utya.gif" alt="About Utya" />
    <div class="card-content">
      Who's Utya?
    </div>

      <div class="utya-info">
<div class="utya-info-text">
  Utya is that little duck on Telegram everyone knows, even if they don’t really know his name.  
  Whenever you search for something and come up empty,  
  he’s the one who shows up to keep things fun.  
  More than just a sticker, Utya has become a symbol of the playful and friendly vibe of Telegram.
</div>

    <img src="/utya-searcher.gif" alt="Utya Searcher" />
  </div>



    <div class="utya-info">
      <div class="utya-info-text">
        Even Utya knows it’s good to let go of the old.  
        When your app data starts piling up, or storage feels heavy,  
        just give things a little refresh — and guess who’s there with a broom and a wink?  
        Yup, it’s Utya.  
        Clearing space never looked this cute.
      </div>

      <img src="/utya-cleaner.gif" alt="Utya Cleaning" />
  </div>

    <div class="utya-info">
<div class="utya-info-text">
  When you enter auto-delete mode Utya appears with a friendly hello note  
  reminding you that even messages deserve a graceful farewell  
  More than just cute he’s your little helper making sure your chats stay fresh and clutter free  
  Always there with a smile and a wave making tidying up feel easy and pleasant
</div>


      <img src="/hello-utya.gif" alt="Utya Cleaning" />
  </div>
  
   <div class="utya-info">
<div class="utya-info-text">
  When you lock your app, Utya makes sure your Telegram stays just yours.  
  So if someone borrows your phone, your chats stay private and secure.  
  Only you can unlock and dive back in.
</div>
      <img src="/utya-lock.gif" alt="Utya Cleaning" />
  </div>

<div class="utya-info">
  <div class="utya-info-text">
    The very first time you open Telegram, something magical happens — <strong>Utya hatches from his little egg</strong> with a cheerful quack just to welcome you!  
    He’s not just adorable — he’s your playful guide to help you explore, chat, and make Telegram feel like home from the very first tap.  
    With Utya by your side, every message starts with a smile and a splash of fun!
  </div>
  <img src="utya-egg.gif" alt="Utya Hatching from Egg" />
</div>



<div class="utya-info">
<div class="utya-info-text">
  The moment you open Telegram for the first time, Utya is there to welcome you with a friendly quack!  
  He’s your quirky guide, ready to help you explore, chat, and connect like never before.  
  With Utya by your side, your Telegram journey starts with a smile and a splash of fun!
</div>
      <img src="utya-detection.gif" alt="Utya Cleaning" />
</div>


<div class="utya-info">
  <div class="utya-info-text">
    When you’re about to invite your friends to Telegram, Utya is the first to crash the party!  
    With his playful grin and friendly quack, he reminds everyone that this hangout is about to get fun and unforgettable.  
    When Utya joins the crew, you know the good times have just begun!
  </div>
  <img src="utya-invite.gif" alt="Utya Joining the Party" />
</div>





  </div>


